<br>
Not really sure how to explain it other than that, but PK has a speedline tutorial up that goes through the process of making a custom speedline brush that might help figure it out. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#CCCCCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/bpolykarbonbbs.showUserPublicProfile?gid=50centwanksta>50centWanksta</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.freewebs.com/50centWanksta/tysonav.JPG" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Karbonite</span><br> <font color=#336699>(2/28/03 5:37 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm35.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=31.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.freewebs.com/50centwanksta/andreself3.JPG height=140 width=130></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: but how?</span><hr size=1>      Thank you for this amazing technique. <p><!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>&quot;It ain't chicken and gravy MAN.&quot;</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#aaaaaa><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/bpolykarbonbbs.showUserPublicProfile?gid=pencilsoldier>Pencil Soldier</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Karbonite</span><br> <font color=#336699>(3/12/03 8:48 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm35.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=31.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.freewebs.com/pencilsoldier/pencils.txt  WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: but how?</span><hr size=1> thanks <p>[Insert witty phrase here.]</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#CCCCCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/bpolykarbonbbs.show